
Installation
------------

 * Copy dot-emacs.el to ~/.emacs
 * Copy directories to ~/Library/Emacs
 * Create ~/Library/Emacs/elisp directory
 * Add next packages to ~/Library/Emacs/elisp:
       * skels:
       	 - Checkout repository
	   darcs get http://hacks-galore.org/jao/darcs/skels
       * margin-mode:
         - Download
           http://www.xanadb.com/margin.el
         - Copy margin.el to margin-mode/
       * JDE:
           * elib-1.0:
             - Download
               http://jdee.sunsite.dk/elib-1.0.tar.gz
             - Decompress to elib/
             - Execute
               EMACS=/Applications/Emacs.app/Contents/MacOS/Emacs make
           * cedet-1.0beta3:
             - Download
               http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/cedet/cedet-1.0beta3b.tar.gz?download
             - Decompress to cedet/
             - Execute
               EMACS=/Applications/Emacs.app/Contents/MacOS/Emacs make
           * jde-2.3.5:
             - Download
               http://jdee.sunsite.dk/jde-latest.tar.gz
             - Decompress to jde/
       * doxymacs-1.8.0:
       	 - Download
           http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/doxymacs/doxymacs-1.8.0.tar.gz?download
         - Decompress to doxymacs/
         - Execute
           EMACS=/Applications/Emacs.app/Contents/MacOS/Emacs ./configure
           make
       * xtla-1.2:
       	 - Download
	   http://download.gna.org/xtla-el/xtla-1.2.tar.gz
	 - Decompress to xtla/
	 - Execute
	   ./configure --with-emacs=/Applications/Emacs.app/Contents/MacOS/Emacs
	   make
